    %section
      %h2 Iaas
      %div
        %br/
      %p Infrastructure as a Service
      %p
        %br>/
        Servers run in the cloud
      %p
        %br/
        %i
          You build and manage EVERYTHING
          %br>/
          (OS, App Servers, Database)
      %p
        %i
          %br/
      %p.fragment{"data-fragment-index" => "0"}
        %i
          %font{:style => "font-size: 42px;"}
            %b Guess how much time you actually spend on your application?
    %section
      %h2 SAAS
      %p
        %br/
      %p
        %span Software as a Service
      %p
        %span
          %br/
      %p Somebody else's application running in the cloud
      %p
        %br/
      %p
        %i You're restricted to the features of their application
      %p
        %i
          %br/
      %p.fragment{"data-fragment-index" => "0"}
        %b
          %font{:color => "#ffffff", :style => "font-size: 42px;"}
            %i Want to change something? Good luck with that...
    %section
